QuestData.Title: Seek Out the Seer
QuestData.Description: We've been watching you, $n.$B$BSeer Malune, keeper of memories, has requested an audience with you, adventurer.$B$BShe has long foretold the coming of a great hero to destroy the lurking shadow. We believe you are that hero.$B$BCome to Duskfall Island, not far south of here, and fulfill your destiny.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Seer Malune on Duskfall Island in Talador.
